{"prompt": "Generate a website for a smart home technology. The website should be elegant and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Aura Smart Home</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #2a3f54;\n            --secondary-color: #3a506b;\n            --accent-color: #5c7b99;\n            --text-color: #ffffff;\n            --background-color: #1a2a3a;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            scroll-behavior: smooth;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 40px 0;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: var(--primary-color);\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            margin-top: 15px;\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        #hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color) 0%, var(--secondary-color) 100%);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 100px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            min-height: 60vh;\n        }\n\n        #hero h2 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            text-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        #hero p {\n            font-size: 1.3em;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: var(--accent-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;\n            border: 2px solid var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: transparent;\n            transform: translateY(-3px);\n            border-color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        .section {\n            padding: 80px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .section h2 {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        .features-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            text-align: left;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            border-left: 5px solid var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        .feature-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(42, 63, 84, 0.4);\n        }\n\n        .feature-item i {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            display: inline-block;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n        }\n\n        .feature-item p {\n            font-size: 1em;\n            color: #ccc;\n        }\n\n        #contact {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 80px 0;\n        }\n\n        #contact h2 {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n        }\n\n        .contact-form {\n            max-width: 600px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            padding: 40px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        .contact-form input,\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 12px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            border: 1px solid var(--accent-color);\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n            font-size: 1em;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form input::placeholder,\n        .contact-form textarea::placeholder {\n            color: #aaa;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button {\n            background-color: var(--accent-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 12px 25px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--accent-color); /* Slightly darker shade on hover */\n            transform: translateY(-2px);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: #ccc;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n\n        footer a {\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n        }\n\n        /* Font Awesome for Icons */\n        /* You'd typically link this in the head, but for a single file, we can embed it */\n        /* For this example, I'll use placeholder text instead of actual icons to keep it simple and avoid external dependencies */\n\n    </style>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Aura Smart Home</h1>\n            <nav>\n                <a href=\"#hero\">Home</a>\n                <a href=\"#features\">Features</a>\n                <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n            </nav>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section id=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Experience the Future of Living</h2>\n            <p>Aura Smart Home seamlessly integrates technology into your life, offering comfort, security, and convenience like never before.</p>\n            <a href=\"#contact\" class=\"cta-button\">Get Started Today</a>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"features\" class=\"section\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Our Smart Solutions</h2>\n            <div class=\"features-grid\">\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-lightbulb\"></i>\n                    <h3>Intelligent Lighting</h3>\n                    <p>Automate your lights, set moods, and save energy with smart, responsive lighting control.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-thermometer-half\"></i>\n                    <h3>Climate Control</h3>\n                    <p>Maintain the perfect temperature and optimize energy usage with intelligent thermostat management.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-lock\"></i>\n                    <h3>Enhanced Security</h3>\n                    <p>Secure your home with smart locks, cameras, and alarm systems, controllable from anywhere.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-volume-up\"></i>\n                    <h3>Seamless Entertainment</h3>\n                    <p>Integrate your audio and video systems for an immersive and effortless entertainment experience.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Let's Build Your Smart Home</h2>\n            <p>Have questions or ready to transform your home? Get in touch with us.</p>\n            <div class=\"contact-form\">\n                <form action=\"#\" method=\"post\">\n                    <input type=\"text\" name=\"name\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n                    <input type=\"email\" name=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n                    <textarea name=\"message\" placeholder=\"Your Message\" rows=\"5\" required></textarea>\n                    <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n                </form>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Aura Smart Home. All rights reserved.</p>\n            <p>Designed with <i class=\"fas fa-heart\" style=\"color: #e74c3c;\"></i> by Your Team</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Basic scroll to section functionality\n        document.querySelectorAll('nav a[href^=\"#\"]').forEach(anchor => {\n            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {\n                e.preventDefault();\n                document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({\n                    behavior: 'smooth'\n                });\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}